---

##  Key Highlights

- Context-aware recommendations (not keyword-based)
- Clean separation of data processing, model logic, and UI
- Robust error handling and score normalization
- Easy to extend with new assessments or models

---

##  Use Case

This system can be used by:
- Recruiters  
- Talent acquisition teams  
- HR platforms  
- Assessment vendors  

to quickly shortlist the **right assessments** for a given role.
